  "title": "Associate Finance Manager",
  "description": "<p>This role, as an Associate Finance Manager, is responsible for managing all finance activities, including quarterly GST filings, corporate tax reporting, and the year-end closing process. To gain a comprehensive understanding of the company’s operations, the position also requires learning customer service–related operating processes and becoming familiar with transactions between the subsidiary and headquarters. Overall, the role demands a strong and holistic understanding of the company’s end-to-end operating activities.</p>",
